Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.98,0:02:18.15,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be3}(Do it, Do it) NO　まだ足らない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.57,0:02:20.95,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be3}I still can go
